  "comment": "LED PAR 60X3W RGB 3in1: Designed for bold performance and refined control, the PAR 160 RGB is a versatile lighting solution for vibrant environments. Powered by 60 x 3W RGB 3-in-1 LEDs, it delivers crisp, high-output color with excellent energy efficiency.\n\nBuilt with a slim die-cast aluminum body and optimized heat sink, it ensures stable performance under demanding conditions. With customizable beam angles (15° to 60°) and dual DMX modes (Basic 4CH / Standard 8CH), it adapts seamlessly to any professional setup.\n\nWhether it's for stage, décor, or ambient applications, the PAR 160 RGB brings precision, flexibility, and vivid impact to every scene.\n\n",
